    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is in the oven, add your <strong>potatoes</strong> to a baking tray and prick them a few times with a sharp knife</p><p>Add a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and put the tray in the oven for 40 min or until cooked through</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
