    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 40 min, remove the dish from the oven and stir through your <strong>crème fraîche</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy free range chicken & mushroom stew</strong></p><p>Remove the potatoes from the oven and crush them firmly with a spatula or the bottom of a plate</p><p>Add a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix it all together – these are your <strong>crushed potatoes</strong></p>",
